{"tid":561760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行政長官發農曆新年賀辭，趁狗年將至大讚警犬","createTime":"2018-02-15T09:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T11:35:32.000Z","uid":33105,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b62a8c872d00688c26ad86ca9e523b33d44f2af","tid":561760,"uid":33105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"　　《經濟通通訊社１５日專訊》狗年將至，行政長官林鄭月娥今日發表的農曆新年賀辭。她表示，很榮幸第一次以行政長官的身分跟公眾拜年。她指，農曆新年是中國人最重視的節日，雖然她跟大家一樣，平常很忙，但每到新年都會抽時間辦年貨和佈置家居，感受節日氣氛。　　她又提到，新一年是狗年，狗忠誠又善解人意，一向是我們的好朋友。她更特別提到，警隊內的警犬，大讚牠們是警察的好拍檔，盡忠職守，協助警察維持治安，讓大家可以安居樂業。　　最後林鄭月娥祝願香港社會在新的一年百業興旺、和諧共融、力求創新、再創輝煌。祝大家萬事如意、身體健康、新年進步。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280215687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280215687&d=IBHhdrFBJbQzXrIVFJJjub%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=05abfdac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280215687</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fc0122a74cf73c85781bfcb537a39da6e72292","tid":561760,"uid":23445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T10:27:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭都幾撚有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d17615dd48d5fe630c25989e4a680fa696d7c9","tid":561760,"uid":103127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11519176c2df3c1fc1465610c226ea7a364f96d1","tid":561760,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hk